summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1736, for the improvement of 7th Avenue North all in the City of Seattle from Prospect Street to the north line of Union Lake Supplemental Addition to the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete sidewalks and wood crosswalks thereon under Ordinance No. 18407 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
